Nigerian football fans will have an opportunity to watch the English Premier League match live in the United Kingdom, courtesy of the Coca-Cola Super Fan Promo.
 
The “Under-The-Crown” EPL promo, which was announced in Lagos at the weekend, kicked off on March 1, 2020, as 10 lucky consumers will be rewarded with an all-expense-paid trip to watch a live English premiership league game and also visit iconic locations in the United Kingdom.
  
According to Coca-Cola, the mouthwatering promotion was rolled out for all football lovers and consumers alike, as a way of appreciating their loyalty and support towards the brand.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .